{"tid":88830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一句令你印象深刻嘅說話","createTime":"2017-01-21T01:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T06:05:16.000Z","uid":26131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56ee217c2285d88316c5016cdabae1f2dac30335","tid":88830,"uid":26131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:37:00.000Z","msg":"有啲句子你聽完 <br />\n其實唔係好特別<br />\n但又會令你記係心入面 記好耐<br />\n<br />\n我記得個陣細個唔識咩係名牌 所以求其係街邊買左個豬鼻圖案嘅斜咩袋 點知原來係冒牌<br />\n之後帶到返學校 啲人就笑我：「你咁窮嘅 要咩老翻袋。」 <br />\n呢句野唔知點解會記咗係心成十年 當時嘅環境仲好深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e381cf558d7f3ca28e350c3a723480778d9821","tid":88830,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:39:50.000Z","msg":"試吓入去中路 葉師奶"},{"pid":"62c26d9eb5b47859ee3803df7d2144494787f80d","tid":88830,"uid":75095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:48:40.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2540ba67fc3bc787c586202383f41bee5d1e9845","tid":88830,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:50:00.000Z","msg":"學校係小中大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c1b874e3a1b04a6619f6b846f9eca99d3e0e13","tid":88830,"uid":26131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學校係小中大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中三黎"},{"pid":"2c22d02f151afca5d120598c7e7cf709f98212f1","tid":88830,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:10:32.000Z","msg":"邊到似你咁得閒"},{"pid":"23da6e3e1e877ac6013e2bf969eb7794707a7656","tid":88830,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:13:14.000Z","msg":"我有名你叫 唔好喂我<br />\n<br />\n依句說話由小五記到依家yr3"},{"pid":"f442ae52a99881f14967892a63634d4f20c63370","tid":88830,"uid":26131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,